Package ohos.agp.components

Interface DatePicker.DateOrder

  • Enclosing class:
    DatePicker

    public static interface DatePicker.DateOrder
    Defines the display format of DatePicker components.

    For example, the date can be displayed in the format of year-month-day, or month-day-year.

    Since:
    1
